         <span class='shortdesc'>What's up for the future?</span>
	 <p>
	   <a href="http://www.onehippo.com">Hippo</a> develops features for customers that have a <a href="http://www.onehippo.com/en/support">Hippo Support License</a>. Our wishlist below contains all the features that we'd like to have one day, and for some we've already implemented parts in the architectural foundations. If you think Hippo CMS is a good match for your situation, but you require any of the features on our wishlist (or something that is *not* on our list :) ), contact <a href="http://www.onehippo.com/en/support">Hippo Support</a> directly. Of course, code donations for any of the features on our wishlist are very very welcome!
	 </p>
